http://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-cel-nfsv4-end2end-data-protection-00

https://www.kernel.org/doc/ols/2008/ols2008v2-pages-151-156.pdf

http://thread.gmane.org/gmane.linux.kernel.aio.general/3904

